channel.title: Best way to trade items between accounts?
channel.description: I can't do bounty hunter trading, the level difference is too great. If anyone can inform me the best way to trade 2m from one account to another, I'd appreciate it. I AM free to play, so I can't do any member things. Thanks.

item.title: Best way to trade items between accounts?
item.dc:creator: @cooper cooper
item.description:
@cooper wrote:

[quote=“PeterMan, post:7, topic:292230”][quote author=cooper link=topic=386089.msg2894782#msg2894782 date=1249146027]

I would love to know if there were a script for rsbot or something that traded over money every 15 minutes.

Can’t seem to find anything though.

There is.

Mind sharing me a link? I can’t seem to find anything

http://www.rsbot.org/vb/showthread.php?t=48022
[/quote]
Thanks man. :)[/quote]
No problem.
